Descend into the terrifyingly beautiful depths of an alien underwater open-world in Subnautica! Discover its breathtaking wonders and hidden dangers as you desperately craft essential gear, construct custom shelters, and scavenge for vital resources – all while striving to survive the crushing pressure and escape this mysterious, aquatic planet.
